Cs_estate_css_v2 - hostage rescue

A remake of Zaphod's "cs_estate"
from the original Counter-Strike.

Map features:

3D Skybox
High Dynamic Range (HDR)
Custom Meshes 
Color Correction
Navigation File (for Bots and hostages)
Soundscapes
Map Overview

Performace Optimzations:
᛫ NoDraw textures
᛫ Area Portals
᛫ Hint Brushes
᛫ Different LODs for the custom Meshes
᛫ Models fade-out
